INFORMATION ON ITEMS:

   There are three different types of items: TANKS,  WEAPONS,  and  TOOLS.  The
   prices move up and down with the player's ranking, in an attempt to keep the
   game more even. All the prices given below assume that  the  buyer  has  the
   average score of all the tanks.

   Sometimes some of the special weapons do not seem to be worth the money, but
   they were all put into the game for a reason - it may simply require  a  bit
   of imagination to use some of them effectively. The descriptions  given  may
   contain some useful ideas.



