SPECIAL MISSIONS

The missions are described from the SHOW MISSIONS option at the main  menu.  It
is up to you to set the game up (types of tanks, number of players, etc .. ) to
fit the mission description. Sometimes there is only one way to set the game up
but other missions allow more freedom and so the setup process becomes part  of
the challenge, and requires your imagination.

If you succeed in any of the missions, a message such as 'mission 1 completed'
will appear on the final score-board in the colour of the corresponding tank.

Missions are not listed in any particular order. Read the descriptions very
carefully or you may miss out on a vital piece of information.










